GET  /api/collections               → 200 | 400 | 401 | 403 | 500  (Bearer)
GET  /api/collections/:id            → 200 | 400 | 401 | 403 | 404 | 500  (Bearer)
POST /api/collections                → 201 | 400 | 401 | 403 | 404 | 500  (Bearer)
PATCH /api/collections/:id          → 200 | 400 | 401 | 403 | 404 | 500  (Bearer)
GET  /api/media                     → 200 | 400 | 401 | 403 | 500  (Bearer)
